                }

                        type: this.next[t],
                        next: this.next[t + 1]
                    }
                }
                ,
                N.prototype.toString = function() {
                    var e = [];
                    return function t(r) {
                        e.push(r);
                        for (var n = 1; n < r.next.length; n += 2)
                            -1 == e.indexOf(r.next[n]) && t(r.next[n])
                    }(this),
                    e.map(function(t, r) {
                        for (var n = r + (t.validEnd ? "*" : " ") + " ", o = 0; o < t.next.length; o += 2)
                            n += (o ? ", " : "") + t.next[o].name + "->" + e.indexOf(t.next[o + 1]);

                    }).join("\n")
                }

                Object.defineProperties(N.prototype, R),
                N.empty = new N(!0);
                var I = function(e, t) {
                    this.string = e,
                    this.nodeTypes = t,
                    this.inline = null,
                    this.pos = 0,

                    "" == this.tokens[0] && this.tokens.unshift()
                }
                  , j = {
                    next: {}
                };
                function D(e) {
                    var t = [];
                    do {
                        t.push(L(e))
                    } while (e.eat("|"));return 1 == t.length ? t[0] : {
                        type: "choice",
                        exprs: t
                    }
                }
                function L(e) {
                    var t = [];
                    do {
                        t.push(F(e))
                    } while (e.next && ")" != e.next && "|" != e.next);return 1 == t.length ? t[0] : {
                        type: "seq",
                        exprs: t
                    }
                }
                function F(e) {
                    for (var t = function(e) {
                        if (e.eat("(")) {
                            var t = D(e);
                            return e.eat(")") || e.err("Missing closing paren"),
                            t
                        }
                        if (!/\W/.test(e.next)) {
                            var r = function(e, t) {
                                var r = e.nodeTypes
                                  , n = r[t];
                                if (n)
                                    return [n];
                                var o = [];
                                for (var i in r) {
                                    var a = r[i];
                                    a.groups.indexOf(t) > -1 && o.push(a)
                                }
                                0 == o.length && e.err("No node type or group '" + t + "' found");
                                return o
                            }(e, e.next).map(function(t) {
                                return null == e.inline ? e.inline = t.isInline : e.inline != t.isInline && e.err("Mixing inline and block content"),
                                {
                                    type: "name",
                                    value: t
                                }
                            });
                            return e.pos++,
                            1 == r.length ? r[0] : {
                                type: "choice",
                                exprs: r
                            }
                        }
                        e.err("Unexpected token '" + e.next + "'")
                    }(e); ; )
                        if (e.eat("+"))
                            t = {
                                type: "plus",
                                expr: t
                            };
                        else if (e.eat("*"))
                            t = {
                                type: "star",
                                expr: t
                            };
                        else if (e.eat("?"))
                            t = {
                                type: "opt",
                                expr: t
                            };
                        else {
                            if (!e.eat("{"))
                                break;
                            t = U(e, t)
                        }
                    return t
                }
                function B(e) {
                    /\D/.test(e.next) && e.err("Expected number, got '" + e.next + "'");
                    var t = Number(e.next);
                    return e.pos++,
                    t
                }
                function U(e, t) {
                    var r = B(e)
                      , n = r;
                    return e.eat(",") && (n = "}" != e.next ? B(e) : -1),
                    e.eat("}") || e.err("Unclosed braced range"),
                    {
                        type: "range",
                        min: r,
                        max: n,
                        expr: t
                    }
                }
                function V(e, t) {
                    return e - t
                }
                function H(e, t) {

                              , s = a.term
                              , c = a.to;
                            s || -1 != r.indexOf(c) || t(c)
                        }
                    }(t),
                    r.sort(V)
                }
                function q(e) {

                        var n = e[r];

                            return null;

                    }

                }

                    }

                ce.prototype.addElement = function(e) {

                            for (var r = 0; r < e.length; r++) {

                                    o[i] = t[n.charCodeAt(i)];
                                e[r][1] = o.join("")
                            }
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.diff_commonPrefix = function(e, t) {
                            if (!e || !t || e.charAt(0) != t.charAt(0))
                                return 0;
                            for (var r = 0, n = Math.min(e.length, t.length), o = n, i = 0; r < o; )
                                e.substring(i, o) == t.substring(i, o) ? i = r = o : n = o,
                                o = Math.floor((n - r) / 2 + r);
                            return o
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.diff_commonSuffix = function(e, t) {
                            if (!e || !t || e.charAt(e.length - 1) != t.charAt(t.length - 1))
                                return 0;
                            for (var r = 0, n = Math.min(e.length, t.length), o = n, i = 0; r < o; )
                                e.substring(e.length - o, e.length - i) == t.substring(t.length - o, t.length - i) ? i = r = o : n = o,
                                o = Math.floor((n - r) / 2 + r);
                            return o
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.diff_commonOverlap_ = function(e, t) {
                            var r = e.length
                              , n = t.length;
                            if (0 == r || 0 == n)
                                return 0;
                            r > n ? e = e.substring(r - n) : r < n && (t = t.substring(0, r));
                            var o = Math.min(r, n);
                            if (e == t)
                                return o;
                            for (var i = 0, a = 1; ; ) {
                                var s = e.substring(o - a)
                                  , c = t.indexOf(s);
                                if (-1 == c)
                                    return i;
                                a += c,
                                0 != c && e.substring(o - a) != t.substring(0, a) || (i = a,
                                a++)
                            }
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_halfMatch_ = function(e, t) {
                            if (this.Diff_Timeout <= 0)
                                return null;
                            var r = e.length > t.length ? e : t
                              , n = e.length > t.length ? t : e;
                            if (r.length < 4 || 2 * n.length < r.length)
                                return null;
                            var o = this;
                            function i(e, t, r) {
                                for (var n, i, a, s, c = e.substring(r, r + Math.floor(e.length / 4)), u = -1, l = ""; -1 != (u = t.indexOf(c, u + 1)); ) {
                                    var f = o.diff_commonPrefix(e.substring(r), t.substring(u))
                                      , p = o.diff_commonSuffix(e.substring(0, r), t.substring(0, u));
                                    l.length < p + f && (l = t.substring(u - p, u) + t.substring(u, u + f),
                                    n = e.substring(0, r - p),
                                    i = e.substring(r + f),
                                    a = t.substring(0, u - p),
                                    s = t.substring(u + f))
                                }
                                return 2 * l.length >= e.length ? [n, i, a, s, l] : null
                            }
                            var a, s, c, u, l, f = i(r, n, Math.ceil(r.length / 4)), p = i(r, n, Math.ceil(r.length / 2));
                            return f || p ? (a = p ? f && f[4].length > p[4].length ? f : p : f,
                            e.length > t.length ? (s = a[0],
                            c = a[1],
                            u = a[2],
                            l = a[3]) : (u = a[0],
                            l = a[1],
                            s = a[2],
                            c = a[3]),
                            [s, c, u, l, a[4]]) : null
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_cleanupSemantic = function(e) {
                            for (var t = !1, r = [], n = 0, o = null, i = 0, a = 0, s = 0, c = 0, u = 0; i < e.length; )
                                0 == e[i][0] ? (r[n++] = i,
                                a = c,
                                s = u,
                                c = 0,
                                u = 0,
                                o = e[i][1]) : (1 == e[i][0] ? c += e[i][1].length : u += e[i][1].length,
                                o && o.length <= Math.max(a, s) && o.length <= Math.max(c, u) && (e.splice(r[n - 1], 0, [-1, o]),

                                n--,
                                i = --n > 0 ? r[n - 1] : -1,
                                a = 0,
                                s = 0,
                                c = 0,
                                u = 0,
                                o = null,
                                t = !0)),
                                i++;
                            for (t && this.diff_cleanupMerge(e),
                            this.diff_cleanupSemanticLossless(e),
                            i = 1; i < e.length; ) {
                                if (-1 == e[i - 1][0] && 1 == e[i][0]) {
                                    var l = e[i - 1][1]
                                      , f = e[i][1]
                                      , p = this.diff_commonOverlap_(l, f)
                                      , d = this.diff_commonOverlap_(f, l);
                                    p >= d ? (p >= l.length / 2 || p >= f.length / 2) && (e.splice(i, 0, [0, f.substring(0, p)]),
                                    e[i - 1][1] = l.substring(0, l.length - p),
                                    e[i + 1][1] = f.substring(p),
                                    i++) : (d >= l.length / 2 || d >= f.length / 2) && (e.splice(i, 0, [0, l.substring(0, d)]),
                                    e[i - 1][0] = 1,
                                    e[i - 1][1] = f.substring(0, f.length - d),
                                    e[i + 1][0] = -1,
                                    e[i + 1][1] = l.substring(d),
                                    i++),
                                    i++
                                }
                                i++
                            }
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_cleanupSemanticLossless = function(e) {
                            function r(e, r) {
                                if (!e || !r)
                                    return 6;
                                var n = e.charAt(e.length - 1)
                                  , o = r.charAt(0)
                                  , i = n.match(t.nonAlphaNumericRegex_)
                                  , a = o.match(t.nonAlphaNumericRegex_)
                                  , s = i && n.match(t.whitespaceRegex_)
                                  , c = a && o.match(t.whitespaceRegex_)
                                  , u = s && n.match(t.linebreakRegex_)
                                  , l = c && o.match(t.linebreakRegex_)
                                  , f = u && e.match(t.blanklineEndRegex_)
                                  , p = l && r.match(t.blanklineStartRegex_);
                                return f || p ? 5 : u || l ? 4 : i && !s && c ? 3 : s || c ? 2 : i || a ? 1 : 0
                            }
                            for (var n = 1; n < e.length - 1; ) {
                                if (0 == e[n - 1][0] && 0 == e[n + 1][0]) {
                                    var o = e[n - 1][1]
                                      , i = e[n][1]
                                      , a = e[n + 1][1]
                                      , s = this.diff_commonSuffix(o, i);
                                    if (s) {
                                        var c = i.substring(i.length - s);
                                        o = o.substring(0, o.length - s),
                                        i = c + i.substring(0, i.length - s),
                                        a = c + a
                                    }
                                    for (var u = o, l = i, f = a, p = r(o, i) + r(i, a); i.charAt(0) === a.charAt(0); ) {
                                        o += i.charAt(0),
                                        i = i.substring(1) + a.charAt(0),
                                        a = a.substring(1);
                                        var d = r(o, i) + r(i, a);
                                        d >= p && (p = d,
                                        u = o,
                                        l = i,
                                        f = a)
                                    }
                                    e[n - 1][1] != u && (u ? e[n - 1][1] = u : (e.splice(n - 1, 1),
                                    n--),
                                    e[n][1] = l,
                                    f ? e[n + 1][1] = f : (e.splice(n + 1, 1),
                                    n--))
                                }
                                n++
                            }
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_cleanupEfficiency = function(e) {
                            for (var t = !1, r = [], n = 0, o = null, i = 0, a = !1, s = !1, c = !1, u = !1; i < e.length; )
                                0 == e[i][0] ? (e[i][1].length < this.Diff_EditCost && (c || u) ? (r[n++] = i,
                                a = c,
                                s = u,
                                o = e[i][1]) : (n = 0,
                                o = null),
                                c = u = !1) : (-1 == e[i][0] ? u = !0 : c = !0,
                                o && (a && s && c && u || o.length < this.Diff_EditCost / 2 && a + s + c + u == 3) && (e.splice(r[n - 1], 0, [-1, o]),

                                n--,
                                o = null,

                                c = u = !1),
                                t = !0)),
                                i++;
                            t && this.diff_cleanupMerge(e)
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_cleanupMerge = function(e) {
                            e.push([0, ""]);
                            for (var t, r = 0, n = 0, o = 0, i = "", a = ""; r < e.length; )
                                switch (e[r][0]) {
                                case 1:
                                    o++,
                                    a += e[r][1],
                                    r++;
                                    break;
                                case -1:
                                    n++,
                                    i += e[r][1],
                                    r++;
                                    break;
                                case 0:
                                    n + o > 1 ? (0 !== n && 0 !== o && (0 !== (t = this.diff_commonPrefix(a, i)) && (r - n - o > 0 && 0 == e[r - n - o - 1][0] ? e[r - n - o - 1][1] += a.substring(0, t) : (e.splice(0, 0, [0, a.substring(0, t)]),
                                    r++),
                                    a = a.substring(t),
                                    i = i.substring(t)),
                                    0 !== (t = this.diff_commonSuffix(a, i)) && (e[r][1] = a.substring(a.length - t) + e[r][1],
                                    a = a.substring(0, a.length - t),
                                    i = i.substring(0, i.length - t))),
                                    0 === n ? e.splice(r - o, n + o, [1, a]) : 0 === o ? e.splice(r - n, n + o, [-1, i]) : e.splice(r - n - o, n + o, [-1, i], [1, a]),
                                    r = r - n - o + (n ? 1 : 0) + (o ? 1 : 0) + 1) : 0 !== r && 0 == e[r - 1][0] ? (e[r - 1][1] += e[r][1],
                                    e.splice(r, 1)) : r++,
                                    o = 0,
                                    n = 0,
                                    i = "",
                                    a = ""
                                }
                            "" === e[e.length - 1][1] && e.pop();

                                0 == e[r - 1][0] && 0 == e[r + 1][0] && (e[r][1].substring(e[r][1].length - e[r - 1][1].length) == e[r - 1][1] ? (e[r][1] = e[r - 1][1] + e[r][1].substring(0, e[r][1].length - e[r - 1][1].length),
                                e[r + 1][1] = e[r - 1][1] + e[r + 1][1],

                                s = !0) : e[r][1].substring(0, e[r + 1][1].length) == e[r + 1][1] && (e[r - 1][1] += e[r + 1][1],

                                e.splice(r + 1, 1),
                                s = !0)),
                                r++;
                            s && this.diff_cleanupMerge(e)
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_xIndex = function(e, t) {
                            var r, n = 0, o = 0, i = 0, a = 0;
                            for (r = 0; r < e.length && (1 !== e[r][0] && (n += e[r][1].length),
                            -1 !== e[r][0] && (o += e[r][1].length),
                            !(n > t)); r++)
                                i = n,
                                a = o;
                            return e.length != r && -1 === e[r][0] ? a : a + (t - i)
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_prettyHtml = function(e) {
                            for (var t = [], r = /&/g, n = /</g, o = />/g, i = /\n/g, a = 0; a < e.length; a++) {
                                var s = e[a][0]
                                  , c = e[a][1].replace(r, "&amp;").replace(n, "&lt;").replace(o, "&gt;").replace(i, "&para;<br>");
                                switch (s) {
                                case 1:
                                    t[a] = '<ins style="background:#e6ffe6;">' + c + "</ins>";
                                    break;
                                case -1:
                                    t[a] = '<del style="background:#ffe6e6;">' + c + "</del>";
                                    break;
                                case 0:
                                    t[a] = "<span>" + c + "</span>"
                                }
                            }
                            return t.join("")
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_text1 = function(e) {
                            for (var t = [], r = 0; r < e.length; r++)
                                1 !== e[r][0] && (t[r] = e[r][1]);
                            return t.join("")
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_text2 = function(e) {
                            for (var t = [], r = 0; r < e.length; r++)
                                -1 !== e[r][0] && (t[r] = e[r][1]);
                            return t.join("")
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_levenshtein = function(e) {
                            for (var t = 0, r = 0, n = 0, o = 0; o < e.length; o++) {
                                var i = e[o][0]
                                  , a = e[o][1];
                                switch (i) {
                                case 1:
                                    r += a.length;
                                    break;
                                case -1:
                                    n += a.length;
                                    break;
                                case 0:
                                    t += Math.max(r, n),
                                    r = 0,
                                    n = 0
                                }
                            }
                            return t += Math.max(r, n)
                        }

                        t.prototype.diff_toDelta = function(e) {
                            for (var t = [], r = 0; r < e.length; r++)
                                switch (e[r][0]) {
                                case 1:
                                    t[r] = "+" + encodeURI(e[r][1]);
                                    break;
                                case -1:
                                    t[r] = "-" + e[r][1].length;
                                    break;
                                case 0:
                                    t[r] = "=" + e[r][1].length
                                }
                            return t.join("\t").replace(/%20/g, " ")
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.diff_fromDelta = function(e, t) {
                            for (var r = [], n = 0, o = 0, i = t.split(/\t/g), a = 0; a < i.length; a++) {
                                var s = i[a].substring(1);
                                switch (i[a].charAt(0)) {
                                case "+":
                                    try {
                                        r[n++] = [1, decodeURI(s)]
                                    } catch (e) {
                                        throw new Error("Illegal escape in diff_fromDelta: " + s)
                                    }
                                    break;
                                case "-":
                                case "=":
                                    var c = parseInt(s, 10);
                                    if (isNaN(c) || c < 0)
                                        throw new Error("Invalid number in diff_fromDelta: " + s);
                                    var u = e.substring(o, o += c);
                                    "=" == i[a].charAt(0) ? r[n++] = [0, u] : r[n++] = [-1, u];
                                    break;
                                default:
                                    if (i[a])
                                        throw new Error("Invalid diff operation in diff_fromDelta: " + i[a])
                                }
                            }
                            if (o != e.length)
                                throw new Error("Delta length (" + o + ") does not equal source text length (" + e.length + ").");
                            return r
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.match_main = function(e, t, r) {
                            if (null == e || null == t || null == r)
                                throw new Error("Null input. (match_main)");
                            return r = Math.max(0, Math.min(r, e.length)),
                            e == t ? 0 : e.length ? e.substring(r, r + t.length) == t ? r : this.match_bitap_(e, t, r) : -1
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.match_bitap_ = function(e, t, r) {
                            if (t.length > this.Match_MaxBits)
                                throw new Error("Pattern too long for this browser.");
                            var n = this.match_alphabet_(t)
                              , o = this;
                            function i(e, n) {
                                var i = e / t.length
                                  , a = Math.abs(r - n);
                                return o.Match_Distance ? i + a / o.Match_Distance : a ? 1 : i
                            }
                            var a = this.Match_Threshold
                              , s = e.indexOf(t, r);
                            -1 != s && (a = Math.min(i(0, s), a),
                            -1 != (s = e.lastIndexOf(t, r + t.length)) && (a = Math.min(i(0, s), a)));
                            var c, u, l = 1 << t.length - 1;
                            s = -1;
                            for (var f, p = t.length + e.length, d = 0; d < t.length; d++) {
                                for (c = 0,
                                u = p; c < u; )
                                    i(d, r + u) <= a ? c = u : p = u,
                                    u = Math.floor((p - c) / 2 + c);
                                p = u;
                                var h = Math.max(1, r - u + 1)
                                  , v = Math.min(r + u, e.length) + t.length
                                  , m = Array(v + 2);
                                m[v + 1] = (1 << d) - 1;
                                for (var g = v; g >= h; g--) {
                                    var y = n[e.charAt(g - 1)];
                                    if (m[g] = 0 === d ? (m[g + 1] << 1 | 1) & y : (m[g + 1] << 1 | 1) & y | (f[g + 1] | f[g]) << 1 | 1 | f[g + 1],
                                    m[g] & l) {
                                        var b = i(d, g - 1);
                                        if (b <= a) {
                                            if (a = b,
                                            !((s = g - 1) > r))
                                                break;
                                            h = Math.max(1, 2 * r - s)
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                if (i(d + 1, r) > a)
                                    break;
                                f = m
                            }
                            return s
                        }
                        ,
                        t.prototype.match_alphabet_ = function(e) {
                            for (var t = {}, r = 0; r < e.length; r++)
                                t[e.charAt(r)] = 0;
                            for (r = 0; r < e.length; r++)
                                t[e.charAt(r)] |= 1 << e.length - r - 1;
                            return t
                        }

                        t.prototype.patch_addContext_ = function(e, t) {
                            if (0 != t.length) {
                                for (var r = t.substring(e.start2, e.start2 + e.length1), n = 0; t.indexOf(r) != t.lastIndexOf(r) && r.length < this.Match_MaxBits - this.Patch_Margin - this.Patch_Margin; )
                                    n += this.Patch_Margin,
                                    r = t.substring(e.start2 - n, e.start2 + e.length1 + n);
                                n += this.Patch_Margin;
                                var o = t.substring(e.start2 - n, e.start2);
                                o && e.diffs.unshift([0, o]);
                                var i = t.substring(e.start2 + e.length1, e.start2 + e.length1 + n);
                                i && e.diffs.push([0, i]),
                                e.start1 -= o.length,
                                e.start2 -= o.length,
                                e.length1 += o.length + i.length,
                                e.length2 += o.length + i.length
                            }
                        }

                        t.prototype.patch_make = function(e, r, n) {
                            var o, i;
                            if ("string" == typeof e && "string" == typeof r && void 0 === n)
                                o = e,
                                (i = this.diff_main(o, r, !0)).length > 2 && (this.diff_cleanupSemantic(i),
                                this.diff_cleanupEfficiency(i));
                            else if (e && "object" == typeof e && void 0 === r && void 0 === n)
                                i = e,
                                o = this.diff_text1(i);
                            else if ("string" == typeof e && r && "object" == typeof r && void 0 === n)
                                o = e,
                                i = r;
                            else {
                                if ("string" != typeof e || "string" != typeof r || !n || "object" != typeof n)
                                    throw new Error("Unknown call format to patch_make.");
                                o = e,
                                i = n
                            }
                            if (0 === i.length)
                                return [];
                            for (var a = [], s = new t.patch_obj, c = 0, u = 0, l = 0, f = o, p = o, d = 0; d < i.length; d++) {
                                var h = i[d][0]
                                  , v = i[d][1];
                                switch (c || 0 === h || (s.start1 = u,
                                s.start2 = l),
                                h) {
                                case 1:
                                    s.diffs[c++] = i[d],
                                    s.length2 += v.length,
                                    p = p.substring(0, l) + v + p.substring(l);
                                    break;
                                case -1:
                                    s.length1 += v.length,
                                    s.diffs[c++] = i[d],
                                    p = p.substring(0, l) + p.substring(l + v.length);
                                    break;
                                case 0:
                                    v.length <= 2 * this.Patch_Margin && c && i.length != d + 1 ? (s.diffs[c++] = i[d],
                                    s.length1 += v.length,
                                    s.length2 += v.length) : v.length >= 2 * this.Patch_Margin && c && (this.patch_addContext_(s, f),
                                    a.push(s),
                                    s = new t.patch_obj,
                                    c = 0,
                                    f = p,
                                    u = l)
                                }
                                1 !== h && (u += v.length),
                                -1 !== h && (l += v.length)
                            }
                            return c && (this.patch_addContext_(s, f),
                            a.push(s)),
                            a
                        }

                        t.prototype.patch_deepCopy = function(e) {
                            for (var r = [], n = 0; n < e.length; n++) {
                                var o = e[n]
                                  , i = new t.patch_obj;
                                i.diffs = [];
                                for (var a = 0; a < o.diffs.length; a++)
                                    i.diffs[a] = o.diffs[a].slice();
                                i.start1 = o.start1,
                                i.start2 = o.start2,
                                i.length1 = o.length1,
                                i.length2 = o.length2,
                                r[n] = i
                            }
                            return r
                        }

                        t.prototype.patch_apply = function(e, t) {
                            if (0 == e.length)
                                return [t, []];
                            e = this.patch_deepCopy(e);
                            var r = this.patch_addPadding(e);
                            t = r + t + r,
                            this.patch_splitMax(e);
                            for (var n = 0, o = [], i = 0; i < e.length; i++) {
                                var a, s, c = e[i].start2 + n, u = this.diff_text1(e[i].diffs), l = -1;
                                if (u.length > this.Match_MaxBits ? -1 != (a = this.match_main(t, u.substring(0, this.Match_MaxBits), c)) && (-1 == (l = this.match_main(t, u.substring(u.length - this.Match_MaxBits), c + u.length - this.Match_MaxBits)) || a >= l) && (a = -1) : a = this.match_main(t, u, c),
                                -1 == a)
                                    o[i] = !1,
                                    n -= e[i].length2 - e[i].length1;
                                else if (o[i] = !0,
                                n = a - c,
                                u == (s = -1 == l ? t.substring(a, a + u.length) : t.substring(a, l + this.Match_MaxBits)))
